item.title: Prayer bpn6013 in Namibia
item.description: ##Makyatiku *Dawn Prayer Oh, Hompa naMushongi wande! Ame ni mupikoye namona mupikoye. Ame narambuka mumakyatiku ghano munguvo dande opo yina pumu Ntungwedi yangurangura yaumwe ghoye yi tunde mukupuma liyuva mumpangero yoye nakurwedimitira shite shayo mughudjuni nauntje kutwara mwavyo ya tanta Mbapira yaVeta doye. Mfumwa kukoye ove Karunga wande, ashi tuna kotoroka mukulimburukwa kushite shaghukonentu ghoye. Tu sheghumwinine ngoli ove Hompa wande ovyo vi tu renkito ashi tuparuke pwa hana ashi ove.
